Purpose
This file implements the summarizer agent.

Linear intent
1. Define local defaults for summary length, confidence, and cost.
2. Expose the agent id as `Summarizer`.
3. Normalize text into words so summarization logic works on clean tokens instead of raw spacing.
4. Reuse a generic `take` helper to cap the number of kept words.
5. Implement `summarize_text` to keep only the first part of a text and add `...` when the text is longer than the budget.
6. Implement `summarize_plan` to flatten a list of steps into one readable summary string.
7. In `run`, accept raw `Text` payloads and turn them into `Summary: ...`.
8. Also accept `Plan` payloads so the summarizer can work after the planner in the long-text path.
9. Attach metrics and a short note describing what was summarized.
10. Reject unsupported payload kinds with a typed error payload.

